{
  "stem": "17845.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in 1948, my parents arrived to-- to Italy from Austria.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we got married.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Smilik was working at the time as a representative for a mizrahi in Milano.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- he was working very hard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because he was helping with the illegal immigration, and when we got married, he-- we didn't spend much of a honeymoon.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because firstly I got appendicitis on the day of my wedding, and nearly went into hospital.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But somehow, seven days afterwards, I did went into hospital to have my operation, my appendix done.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he wasn't with me, because he had to go to Genoa.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because there was an illegal transport to be sent to Israel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And everything was illegal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he used to send me cards.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I still got them from Genoa, or from Venice, or from Napoli.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he couldn't say why he's not-- so he used to send me, because of that, I can't come home.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And on the folder was a storm or something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he used to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I remember in hospital, the Italian women were so upset, it's such a young couple, and the husband is not with you.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I could-- I couldn't explain to them why he is not with me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because what he was doing was illegal, and the Aliyah Bet used-- used to meet the transports of Jews who was running away from Poland, and from Austria, and from Czechoslovakia, and from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they used to go out in the middle of the night to meet him and help them, to-- to go over the station, from Italy to the vessels to take them to Israel.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I wasn't working, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Albiate, well only our kibbutz, about 180 people in our-- in our villa.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
